#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1
msgid "YAML Configuration Syntax"
msgstr "YAML配置语法"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:3
msgid ""
"The configuration file is a YAML file to initialize the environment. It "
"contains the configuration parameters to simulate and visualize the world, "
"obstacle, and robot. You can customize the scenario and define the behavior "
"of the objects simply by using the parameters."
msgstr ""
"配置文件是用于初始化环境的 YAML 文件。它包含用于模拟和可视化世界、障碍物和机"
"器人的配置参数。你只需通过这些参数即可自定义场景并定义对象的行为。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:7
msgid "Configuration Overview"
msgstr "配置总览"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:9
msgid ""
"A complete IR-SIM scene is described by up to four top-level keys: `world`, "
"`robot`, `obstacle`, and `gui`. **`robot` and `obstacle` accept the same per-"
"object keys**, while factory defaults can differ by object type and "
"kinematics, such as `role`, color, state dimension, and image description. "
"Expand the interactive tree below to explore every key with its type and "
"default; every key is optional unless its default is `unset`. Click a "
"section's **full docs ›** link to jump to the detailed description."
msgstr ""
"一个完整的 IR-SIM 场景由最多四个顶层键描述 —— `world`、`robot`、`obstacle` "
"和 `gui`。**`robot` 和 `obstacle` 接受相同的对象级键**，但工厂默认值会因对象"
"类型和运动学而异，例如 `role`、颜色、状态维度和图像描述。展开下方的交互式树即"
"可浏览每个键及其类型和默认值；除非默认值为 `unset`，否则所有键均为可选。点击"
"各部分的 **full docs ›** 链接可跳转到详细说明。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:452
msgid ""
"This tree is a quick map: click any key to jump to its full description. For "
"prose, examples, and edge cases, see the per-section docs below."
msgstr ""
"该树是一个快速导览 —— 点击任意键即可跳转到它的完整说明。完整的说明、示例和边"
"界情况请参见下方各部分的文档。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:457
msgid "Quick Start Example"
msgstr "快速上手示例"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:459
msgid ""
"The configuration file is divided into three main sections: `world`, "
"`robot`, and `obstacle`. Here's a minimal working example you can copy and "
"adapt:"
msgstr ""
"配置文件主要分为三个部分：`world`、`robot` 和 `obstacle`。下面是一个可直接复"
"制并修改的最小可用示例："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:0
msgid "Basic Configuration"
msgstr "基础配置"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:507
msgid "**Key Configuration Guidelines:**"
msgstr "**关键内容配置指南**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:509
msgid ""
"To include several robots or obstacles in the configuration file, add "
"separate entries under the robot and obstacle sections using `-` for each "
"additional item."
msgstr ""
"要在配置文件中包含多个机器人或障碍物，请在 robot 和 obstacle 部分下添加单独的"
"条目，并使用 `-` 标记每个添加的条目。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:510
msgid ""
"Parameters such as distribution, shape, behavior, group_behavior, and "
"kinematics must be formatted as `{key: value}` pairs. Ensure that each "
"dictionary includes the `name` key; omitting name will result in a None "
"value for that parameter."
msgstr ""
"distribution、shape、behavior、group_behavior 和 kinematics 等参数必须写成 "
"`{key: value}` 字典形式。请确保每个字典都包含 `name` 键；省略 name 会使该参数"
"取值为 None。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:511
msgid ""
"When dealing with multiple objects (i.e., when the number is greater than "
"1), utilize the `distribution` parameter to define how these objects are "
"distributed."
msgstr ""
"当处理多个对象（即数量大于 1）时，利用 `distribution` 参数来定义这些对象的摆"
"放位置的分布方式。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:512
msgid ""
"By default, all objects within the same group share identical "
"configurations. To customize individual objects within a group, add sub-"
"parameters using `-`. Any additional objects not explicitly configured will "
"inherit the settings of the last specified object in the group."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，同一组内的所有对象共享相同的配置。要单独自定义组内的某个对象，可"
"使用 `-` 添加子参数。未显式配置的其余对象会继承组中最后一个已指定对象的设置。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:513
msgid ""
"Object-level `name` is optional and identifies each object. If omitted, it "
"defaults to `\"<role>_<id>\"` (e.g., `robot_0`, `obstacle_3`). Names must be "
"unique across all objects; duplicates raise an error during environment "
"initialization. Do not confuse object-level `name` with the `name` keys used "
"inside dictionaries like `shape`, `kinematics`, or `behavior` (which "
"indicate component types)."
msgstr ""
"对象级 `name` 是可选的，用于标识每个对象。若省略，默认值为 `\"<role>_<id>\"`"
"（例如 `robot_0`、`obstacle_3`）。名称在所有对象间必须唯一；重复会在环境初始"
"化时报错。请勿将对象级 `name` 与 `shape`、`kinematics`、`behavior` 等字典内部"
"的 `name` 键混淆（后者表示组件类型）。"

