#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:543
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:746
msgid "Detailed Parameter Descriptions"
msgstr "参数详解"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:0
msgid "**world properties**"
msgstr "**world 属性**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:549
msgid "**`name`** (`str`, default: `\"world\"`)"
msgstr "**`name`**（`str`，默认： `\"world\"`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:550
msgid ""
"Defines the name of the world used in the simulation. This can be useful for "
"identifying different simulation environments."
msgstr "定义仿真使用的世界名称，便于区分不同环境。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:553
msgid "**`height`** (`float`, default: `10`)"
msgstr "**`height`**（`float`，默认 `10`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:554
msgid ""
"Specifies the vertical size of the world in units of meters in the Y-axis "
"direction plotted on the screen."
msgstr "指定世界在屏幕 Y 轴方向的垂直尺寸（米）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:557
msgid "**`width`** (`float`, default: `10`)"
msgstr "**`width`**（`float`，默认 `10`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:558
msgid ""
"Specifies the horizontal size of the world in units of meters in the X-axis "
"direction plotted on the screen."
msgstr "指定世界在屏幕 X 轴方向的水平尺寸（米）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:561
msgid "**`step_time`** (`float`, default: `0.1`)"
msgstr "**`step_time`**（`float`，默认 `0.1`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:562
msgid "Determines the time interval between each simulation step."
msgstr "决定仿真每一步之间的时间间隔。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:564
msgid ""
"**Performance Impact**: A smaller `step_time` results in a higher simulation "
"frequency (e.g., `0.1` seconds corresponds to 10 Hz) but needs longer time "
"to run the simulation."
msgstr ""
"**性能影响**：`step_time` 越小仿真频率越高（如 0.1 秒即 10 Hz），但仿真耗时也"
"更长。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:567
msgid "**`sample_time`** (`float`, default: `step_time`)"
msgstr "**`sample_time`**（`float`，默认与 `step_time` 相同）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:568
msgid ""
"Defines the time interval for rendering the simulation and extracting data. "
"This controls how frequently visual updates and data recordings occur. If "
"not specified, defaults to the value of `step_time`."
msgstr ""
"定义渲染与数据采集的时间间隔，决定可视化更新与记录的频率。未指定时默认等于 "
"`step_time`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:571
msgid "**`offset`** (`list` of `float`, default: `[0, 0]`)"
msgstr "**`offset`**（`float` 列表，默认 `[0, 0]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:572
msgid ""
"Sets the initial positional offset of the world on the X and Y axes. This is "
"useful for positioning the world within a larger coordinate system or for "
"relative placement."
msgstr "设置世界在 X、Y 轴上的初始偏移，便于在更大坐标系中定位或相对放置。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:0
msgid "**world mode**"
msgstr "**world 模式**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:579
msgid "**`control_mode`** (`str`, default: `\"auto\"`)"
msgstr "**`control_mode`** (`str`, 默认： `\"auto\"`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:580
msgid "Configures how the objects in the simulation are controlled:"
msgstr "配置仿真中对象的被控方式："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:582
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:590
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:778
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:943
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1113
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1154
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1294
msgid "**Options:**"
msgstr "**选项:**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:583
msgid ""
"`auto`: Automatic control by the input velocities defined in python script "
"or behavior in the YAML file."
msgstr ""
"`auto`：通过 Python 脚本中定义的输入速度或 YAML 文件中的行为进行自动控制。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:584
msgid ""
"`keyboard`: Manual control via keyboard inputs. The key inputs are defined "
"in the file."
msgstr "`keyboard`：通过键盘输入进行手动控制。按键输入在文件中定义。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:587
msgid "**`collision_mode`** (`str`, default: `\"stop\"`)"
msgstr "**`collision_mode`** (`str`, 默认： `\"stop\"`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:588
msgid "Defines how collisions between objects are handled in the simulation:"
msgstr "定义仿真中对象碰撞的处理方式："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:591
msgid "`stop`: Stops the movement of objects upon collision. (default)"
msgstr "`stop`：发生碰撞时立即停止（默认）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:592
msgid ""
"`unobstructed`: Allows objects to pass through each other without "
"consideration of any collision."
msgstr "`unobstructed`：允许对象彼此穿过，不考虑任何碰撞。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:593
msgid ""
"`unobstructed_obstacles`: Only allows obstacles to pass through each other "
"without consideration of any collision. The robots will stop when they are "
"in collision with the obstacles."
msgstr ""
"`unobstructed_obstacles`：仅允许障碍物彼此穿过而不考虑碰撞；机器人与障碍物发"
"生碰撞时仍会停止。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:596
msgid "**`status`** (`str`, default: `\"None\"`)"
msgstr "**`status`** (`str`, 默认值： `\"None\"`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:597
msgid ""
"Sets the label displayed before the first completed simulation step. It "
"accepts any string and defaults to the `\"None\"` sentinel."
msgstr ""
"设置第一个完整仿真步之前显示的标签。该字段接受任意字符串，默认使用 "
"`\"None\"` 哨兵值。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:599
msgid ""
"After each completed step, IR-SIM replaces this label with the computed "
"runtime status, such as `\"Running\"`, `\"Arrived\"`, or `\"Collision\"`."
msgstr ""
"每个完整仿真步结束后，IR-SIM 会用计算得到的运行时状态替换该标签，例如 "
"`\"Running\"`、`\"Arrived\"` 或 `\"Collision\"`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:601
msgid ""
"**Note**: This setting does not control execution. In particular, `status: "
"\"Pause\"` does not start a paused simulation. Use `env.pause()` and "
"`env.resume()` to control execution, and `env.done()` to check completion."
msgstr ""
"**注意**：此设置不控制执行。尤其是，`status: \"Pause\"` 不会让仿真以暂停状态"
"启动。请使用 `env.pause()` 和 `env.resume()` 控制执行，并使用 `env.done()` 检"
"查是否完成。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:0
msgid "**world map**"
msgstr "**world 地图**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:608
msgid ""
"**`obstacle_map`** (`dict`, `str`, `ndarray`, or `null`, default: `None`)"
msgstr ""
"**`obstacle_map`**（`dict`、`str`、`ndarray` 或 `null`，默认值：`None`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:609
msgid ""
"Occupancy grid source. **Canonical form is a generator spec dict** with "
"``name``; other types are convenience/backward compat."
msgstr ""
"占据栅格来源。**标准形式是带 ``name`` 的生成器配置字典**；其他类型为便捷写法/"
"向后兼容。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:611
msgid ""
"**Generator spec** (`dict`): ``name`` identifies the generator. ``name: "
"image`` with ``path`` (e.g. ``'cave.png'``) loads an image; grid size from "
"the image. ``name: perlin`` (and others) require ``resolution``; grid size = "
"world size / resolution. See [Configure grid map](../usage/"
"configure_grid_map.md). To add a new generator, see [Adding a new map "
"generator](../usage/configure_grid_map.md#adding-a-new-map-generator)."
msgstr ""
"**生成器配置**（`dict`）：``name`` 标识生成器。``name: image`` 配合 ``path``"
"（例如 ``'cave.png'``）从图像加载，栅格大小取自图像。``name: perlin``（及其"
"他）需要 ``resolution``；栅格大小 = 世界大小 / resolution。参见 [配置栅格地"
"图](../usage/configure_grid_map.md)。要新增生成器，参见 [新增地图生成器](../"
"usage/configure_grid_map.md#adding-a-new-map-generator)。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:612
msgid ""
"**Image path** (`str`): Treated as ``{ name: image, path: obstacle_map }`` "
"(backward compat)."
msgstr ""
"**图像路径**（`str`）：等价于 ``{ name: image, path: obstacle_map }``（向后兼"
"容）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:613
msgid ""
"**Occupancy grid** (`ndarray`): Programmatic use only. Float 0–100; world "
"size must match grid shape."
msgstr ""
"**占据栅格**（`ndarray`）：仅供编程方式使用。浮点值 0–100；世界大小必须与栅格"
"形状匹配。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:614
msgid "**`null`**: No obstacle map (empty world)."
msgstr "**`null`**：无障碍物地图（空世界）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:616
msgid ""
"**Available Maps**: We provide some example maps in the `irsim/world/map` "
"folder and you can also use your own map by 3D datasets like [HM3D](https://"
"aihabitat.org/datasets/hm3d/), [MatterPort3D](https://niessner.github.io/"
"Matterport/), [Gibson](http://gibsonenv.stanford.edu/database/), etc. See "
"[here](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/tree/features/irsim/world/map/"
"binary_map_generator_hm3d) for more details."
msgstr ""
"**可用地图**：我们在 `irsim/world/map` 文件夹中提供了一些示例地图，你也可以使"
"用来自 [HM3D](https://aihabitat.org/datasets/hm3d/)、[MatterPort3D](https://"
"niessner.github.io/Matterport/)、[Gibson](http://gibsonenv.stanford.edu/"
"database/) 等 3D 数据集的自定义地图。更多细节见 [此处](https://github.com/"
"hanruihua/ir-sim/tree/features/irsim/world/map/binary_map_generator_hm3d)。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:632
msgid "**`mdownsample`** (`int`, default: `1`)"
msgstr "**`mdownsample`** (`int`, 默认值： `1`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:633
msgid "Sets the downsampling factor for the obstacle map image."
msgstr "设置障碍物地图图像的降采样系数。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:635
msgid ""
"**Performance Tip**: A higher value reduces the resolution of the obstacle "
"map, which can optimize the simulation performance by decreasing "
"computational load."
msgstr ""
"**提示**：更高的取值会降低障碍地图的分辨率，减小计算负载，从而提升仿真性能。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:638
msgid "**`fog_map`** (`bool`, default: `false`)"
msgstr "**`fog_map`** (`bool`, 默认值： `false`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:639
msgid ""
"Enables a **fog-of-map** overlay (`FogMap`) covering the whole world. Every "
"cell starts grey (unexplored). Each robot reveals cells along its lidar's "
"line of sight, or within its field-of-view sector ([`fov`](#p-o-fov) / "
"`fov_radius`) when it has no lidar, so the explored region grows as the "
"robot navigates; revealed cells become transparent and the underlying map "
"shows through (free space white, obstacles black, unknown grey). The "
"explored mask is updated every step even when headless, so it can also be "
"used as an exploration/coverage signal "
"(`env._world.fog_map.explored_ratio`). See the `usage/24fog_world` example."
msgstr ""
"启用覆盖整个世界的**地图迷雾**叠加层（`FogMap`）。每个栅格初始为灰色（未探"
"索）。每个机器人沿其激光雷达视线揭示栅格，若没有激光雷达，则在其视场扇形"
"（[`fov`](#p-o-fov) / `fov_radius`）内揭示，因此随着机器人移动，已探索区域不"
"断扩大；已揭示的栅格变为透明，露出底层地图（空闲为白色、障碍为黑色、未知为灰"
"色）。即使无显示（headless），已探索掩码也会每步更新，可用作探索/覆盖率信号"
"（`env._world.fog_map.explored_ratio`）。参见 `usage/24fog_world` 示例。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:642
msgid ""
"**`fog_map_resolution`** (`float`, default: obstacle map cell size, else "
"`0.1`)"
msgstr ""
"**`fog_map_resolution`** (`float`, 默认值：障碍地图栅格尺寸，否则为 `0.1`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:643
msgid ""
"Fog cell size in metres, used only when `fog_map: true`. When omitted it "
"matches the obstacle map's cell size, so the fog grid aligns with the map; "
"it falls back to `0.1` m when there is no obstacle map. Finer values give a "
"smoother reveal but cost more memory/time; coarser values are faster."
msgstr ""
"迷雾栅格的尺寸（米），仅在 `fog_map: true` 时使用。省略时与障碍地图的栅格尺寸"
"一致，使迷雾栅格与地图对齐；若无障碍地图则回退为 `0.1` 米。取值越细腻揭示越平"
"滑，但占用更多内存/时间；取值越粗糙则越快。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:0
msgid "**world visualization**"
msgstr "**world 可视化**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:650
msgid "**`plot`** (`dict`, default: `{}`)"
msgstr "**`plot`** (`dict`, 默认值： `{}`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:651
msgid "Specifies the plotting options for initializing the plot of the world."
msgstr "指定初始化世界绘图时可用的绘制选项。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:653
msgid "**Visualization Options:**"
msgstr "**可视化选项：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:654
msgid ""
"`saved_figure`: Default `dpi` is `100`; default format is `png`; default "
"bbox_inches is `tight`. See [matplotlib.pyplot.savefig](https://"
"matplotlib.org/stable/api/_as_gen/matplotlib.pyplot.savefig.html) for more "
"details."
msgstr ""
"`saved_figure`：默认 `dpi` 为 `100`；默认格式为 `png`；默认 bbox_inches 为 "
"`tight`。更多细节参见 [matplotlib.pyplot.savefig](https://matplotlib.org/"
"stable/api/_as_gen/matplotlib.pyplot.savefig.html)。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:655
msgid ""
"`figure_pixels`: Width and height of the figure in pixels. Default is "
"`[1000, 800]`."
msgstr "`figure_pixels`: 图像的像素宽和高，默认值为`[1000, 800]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:656
msgid "`show_title`: Whether to show the plot title. Default is `True`."
msgstr "`show_title`: 是否显示图表标题，默认是`True`."

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:657
msgid ""
"`title`: Custom title for the plot. If not specified, shows simulation time "
"and status."
msgstr "`title`：自定义图表标题；若未指定，则显示仿真时间与当前状态。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:658
msgid "`no_axis`: Whether to show the axis. Default is `False`."
msgstr "`no_axis`： 是否显示坐标轴，默认是`False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:659
msgid "`tight`: Whether to use tight layout. Default is `True`."
msgstr "`tight`: 是否使用紧凑布局，默认是`True`."

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:660
msgid ""
"`viewpoint`: Controls the center of the camera/viewport. Default is `null`."
msgstr "`viewpoint`: 控制相机（视角）的中心位置，默认值为`null`."

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:661
msgid "`null`: Use the initial world bounds (no automatic panning)."
msgstr "`null`：使用初始的世界边界，不进行自动移动"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:662
msgid "`[x, y]`: Keep the viewport centered at the fixed point `[x, y]`."
msgstr "`[x, y]`：视角始终以固定点`[x, y]`为中心"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:663
msgid ""
"`\"<object_name>\"`: Follow the object with that name (dynamic panning), "
"e.g., `\"robot_0\"`."
msgstr "`\"<object_name>\"`：跟随该名称的对象进行动态平移，例如`\"robot_0\"`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:675
msgid "Complete World Configuration Example"
msgstr "完整世界配置示例"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:701
msgid ""
"**`obstacle_map`**: Replace `\"path/to/map.png\"` with the actual file path "
"to your obstacle map image. Ensure that the image is in a compatible format "
"(e.g., PNG, JPEG) and properly represents obstacle locations."
msgstr ""
"**`obstacle_map`**：将 `\"path/to/map.png\"` 替换为你的障碍物地图图像的实际文"
"件路径。请确保图像为兼容格式（如 PNG、JPEG）并正确表示障碍物位置。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:707
