"All `robot` and `obstacle` entities in the simulation are configured as "
"objects with similar parameters but may have different default values. This "
"section outlines the configuration parameters available for these objects."
msgstr ""
"仿真中的 `robot` 与 `obstacle` 都作为对象进行配置，参数结构类似但默认值可能不"
"同。本节介绍这些对象可用的配置项。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:712
