"Unique identifier for the object. If omitted, auto-assigned as "
"`\"<role>_<id>\"`. Supports a list when `number > 1`."
msgstr ""
"对象的唯一标识符；若省略，则会自动分配为`\"<role>_<id>\"`。当`number > 1`时支"
"持参数列表。"

