msgid "`{name: manual}`"
msgstr "`{name: manual}`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:700
msgid ""
"Defines how multiple objects are distributed. Support name: `manual`, "
"`random`, `circle`"
msgstr "定义多个对象的分布方式。支持的分布方式有：`manual`, `random`, `circle`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:700
