msgstr "**`role`** — 对象类型（`robot`、`obstacle`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:765
msgid "**`number`** (`int`, default: `1`)"
msgstr "**`number`** (`int`, 默认值： `1`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:766
msgid ""
"Specifies the number of objects to create using the given configuration."
msgstr "指定使用该配置创建的对象数量。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:775
msgid ""
"**`distribution`** (`dict`, default: `{name: manual}`) ([source](https://ir-"
"sim.readthedocs.io/en/dev/"
"irsim.world.html#irsim.world.object_factory.ObjectFactory.generate_state_list))"
msgstr ""
"**`distribution`**（`dict`，默认值：`{name: manual}`）（[源码](https://ir-"
"sim.readthedocs.io/en/dev/"
"irsim.world.html#irsim.world.object_factory.ObjectFactory.generate_state_list)）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:776
msgid ""
"Defines how multiple objects are spatially distributed when `number` is "
"greater than `1`."
msgstr "当`number`大于1时，定义多个对象在空间中的分布方式。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:779
msgid "`'manual'`: Manually specify initial states and goals for each object."
msgstr "`'manual'`:手动为每个对象指定初始状态和目标"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:780
msgid ""
"In this case, the `state` (or goal) parameters must be provided for each "
"object. If the provided list is shorter than the number of objects, the last "
"state (or goal) is repeated."
msgstr ""
"这种模式下必须为每个对象提供`state`（或目标）参数；如果提供的列表长度少于对象"
"数量，则最后一个状态（或目标）会被重复使用。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:789
msgid ""
"`'random'`: Randomly distribute objects within specified ranges. Points are "
"rejection-sampled so every pair is at least `min_distance` apart in the xy "
"plane. Optional parameters:"
msgstr ""
"`'random'`: 在指定范围内随机分布对象。采样过程采用拒绝采样，保证任意两点在 "
"xy 平面上的距离至少为 `min_distance`。可选参数："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:790
msgid ""
"`range_low` (list): Lower bounds `[x, y, theta]` for random distribution. "
"Defaults to the world bounds inset by `0.5`, i.e. `[offset_x + 0.5, offset_y "
"+ 0.5, -pi]`."
msgstr ""
"`range_low` (list): 随机分布的下界 `[x, y, theta]`。默认值为世界边界向内缩进 "
"`0.5`，即 `[offset_x + 0.5, offset_y + 0.5, -pi]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:791
msgid ""
"`range_high` (list): Upper bounds `[x, y, theta]` for random distribution. "
"Defaults to `[offset_x + width - 0.5, offset_y + height - 0.5, pi]`."
msgstr ""
"`range_high` (list): 随机分布的上界 `[x, y, theta]`。默认值为 `[offset_x + "
"width - 0.5, offset_y + height - 0.5, pi]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:792
msgid ""
"`min_distance` (float): Minimum pairwise xy distance between sampled points. "
"Default is `1.0`."
msgstr ""
"`min_distance` (float): 采样点之间在 xy 平面上的最小两两距离。默认值为 "
"`1.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:799
msgid ""
"`'circle'`: Arrange objects in a circular formation around a specified "
"center. Optional parameters:"
msgstr "`'circle'`:将对象以圆形阵列排布在指定中心周围。可选参数："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:800
msgid ""
"`center` (list): Center coordinates `[x, y, theta]` of the circle. Defaults "
"to the world center `[offset_x + width / 2, offset_y + height / 2, 0]`."
msgstr ""
"`center` (list): 圆心坐标 `[x, y, theta]`。默认值为世界中心 `[offset_x + "
"width / 2, offset_y + height / 2, 0]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:801
msgid ""
"`radius` (float): Radius of the circle. Defaults to `min(width, height) / 2 "
"- 0.5` so the circle sits inside the world with a small margin."
msgstr ""
"`radius` (float): 圆的半径。默认值为 `min(width, height) / 2 - 0.5`，使圆形排"
"布留有少量边距。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:809
msgid ""
"**`state`** (`list` of `float`, default: `[1, 1, 0]` for manual distribution)"
msgstr "**`state`**（`float` 列表，手动分布时默认：`[1, 1, 0]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:810
msgid ""
"Defines the initial state of the object, typically in the format `[x, y, "
"theta]`, where `theta` represents the orientation in radians. If the "
"provided state has more elements than required, extra elements are "
"truncated; if fewer, missing values are filled with zeros. Random and circle "
"distributions generate states from their distribution parameters."
msgstr ""
"定义对象的初始状态，通常为 `[x, y, theta]` 格式，其中 `theta` 表示以弧度为单"
"位的朝向。若提供的状态元素多于所需，多余的会被截断；若不足，缺失值以零补齐。"
"随机分布和圆形分布会根据其分布参数生成状态。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:818
msgid "**`velocity`** (`list` of `float`, default: `[0] * action_dim`)"
msgstr "**`velocity`**（`float` 列表，默认：`[0] * action_dim`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:819
msgid ""
"Specifies the initial velocity (list) of the object. The length must match "
"the kinematics action dimension. The format depends on the kinematics model:"
msgstr ""
"指定对象的初始速度（列表）。长度须与运动学动作维度匹配。格式取决于运动学模"
"型："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:821
msgid "**Format by Kinematics:**"
msgstr "**运动学模型的格式：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:822
msgid ""
"For `'diff'`: `[v, omega]`, where `v` is linear velocity and `omega` is "
"angular velocity."
msgstr "`'diff'`模型参数由`[v, omega]`构成， 其中 `v` 线速度，`omega`角速度。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:823
msgid ""
"For `'omni'`: `[forward, lateral]`, body-frame velocities (forward and "
"lateral relative to heading)."
msgstr ""
"`'omni'`模型参数由`[forward, lateral]`构成，为机体坐标系下的速度（相对于朝向"
"的前进和横向速度）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:824
msgid ""
"For `'acker'`: Typically `[v, phi]`, where `v` is linear velocity and `phi` "
"is steering angle."
msgstr ""
"`'acker'`模型参数通常由`[v, phi]`构成，其中 `v` 是线速度，`phi`是转向角。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:832
msgid ""
"**`goal`** (`list` of `float` or `list` of `list` of `float`, default: `[1, "
"9, 0]` for manual distribution)"
msgstr ""
"**`goal`**（`float` 列表或 `float` 列表的列表，手动分布时默认：`[1, 9, 0]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:833
msgid ""
"Sets the target state or position the object should move toward. Used in "
"conjunction with behaviors to guide the object's navigation. The format is "
"`[x, y, theta]` or `[[x, y, theta], [x, y, theta], ...]` for multiple goals. "
"Random and circle distributions generate goals from their distribution "
"parameters."
msgstr ""
"设置对象应移动到的目标状态或位置。与行为配合使用以引导对象导航。格式为 `[x, "
"y, theta]`，或多目标时为 `[[x, y, theta], [x, y, theta], ...]`。随机分布和圆"
"形分布会根据其分布参数生成目标。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:840
msgid ""
"**Note**: For multiple goals for the single object (Pay attention to the "
"difference between the single goal for multiple objects and multiple goals "
"for the single object):"
msgstr ""
"**注意**：对于单个对象的多个目标（注意区分多个对象的单个目标与单个对象的多个"
"目标）："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:849
msgid "**`state_dim`** (`int`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`state_dim`** (`int`, 默认值： `None`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:850
msgid ""
"Explicitly defines the dimension of the state vector. When not specified, "
"this is automatically inferred from the kinematics model. For most use "
"cases, the default inference is sufficient."
msgstr ""
"显式定义状态向量的维度。若未指定，则自动从运动学模型推断。对于大多数使用场"
"景，默认推断即可满足需求。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:852
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:865
msgid "**Common Values:**"
msgstr "**常用值：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:853
msgid "`3`: For 2D position and orientation `[x, y, theta]`"
msgstr "`3`: 2D的位置和朝向角 `[x, y, theta]`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:854
msgid ""
"`4`: For vehicles with additional state (e.g., Ackermann with `[x, y, theta, "
"steer_angle]`)"
msgstr ""
"`4`：对于具有额外状态的车辆（例如 Ackermann 模型的`[x, y, theta, "
"steer_angle]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:862
msgid "**`vel_dim`** (`int`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`vel_dim`** (`int`, 默认值： `None`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:863
msgid ""
"Explicitly defines the dimension of the velocity vector. When not specified, "
"this is automatically inferred from the kinematics model. The velocity "
"dimension depends on the control inputs for the specific kinematics."
msgstr ""
"显式定义速度向量的维度。若未指定，则自动从运动学模型推断。速度维度取决于特定"
"运动学模型的控制输入。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:866
msgid ""
"`2`: For differential drive `[v, omega]` or omnidirectional `[forward, "
"lateral]`"
msgstr "`2`：对于差速驱动`[v, omega]`或全向 `[forward, lateral]`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:867
msgid ""
"`3`: For omnidirectional with angular control `[forward, lateral, yaw_rate]`"
msgstr "`3`：对于带角速度控制的全向模型 `[forward, lateral, yaw_rate]`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:875
msgid "**`group`** (`int`, default: `0`)"
msgstr "**`group`**（`int`，默认 `0`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:876
msgid ""
"Specifies a group identifier for organizational purposes, allowing objects "
"to be categorized and managed together. Objects with the same group ID can "
"be treated as a cohesive unit for certain operations."
msgstr ""
"指定用于组织目的的分组标识符，允许对象被分类和管理。具有相同分组 ID 的对象可"
"作为一个整体用于某些操作。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:884
msgid "**`group_name`** (`str`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`group_name`** (`str`, 默认值为: `None`)"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:885
msgid ""
"Specifies a group name for organizational purposes, allowing objects to be "
"categorized and managed together. Objects with the same group name can be "
"treated as a cohesive unit for certain operations."
msgstr ""
"用于组织目的指定分组名称，使对象能够被分类并统一管理。具有相同分组名称的对象"
"在某些操作中可作为一个整体进行处理。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:893
msgid "**`name`** (`str` or `list` of `str`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`name`**（`str` 或 `str` 列表，默认 `None`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:894
msgid ""
"Sets a unique identifier for the object. If not provided, the name defaults "
"to \"<role>_<id>\" (e.g., `robot_0`, `obstacle_3`). Names must be unique "
"across all objects in the environment; duplicates will raise a `ValueError` "
"during initialization."
msgstr ""
"为对象设置唯一标识符。若未提供，名称默认为 \"<role>_<id>\"（例如 `robot_0`、"
"`obstacle_3`）。名称在环境中所有对象间必须唯一；重复会在初始化时抛出 "
"`ValueError`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:896
msgid ""
"When creating multiple objects (`number > 1`), you can provide a list of "
"names. If the provided list is shorter than the number of objects, the last "
"name is repeated for remaining objects; ensure uniqueness to avoid errors."
msgstr ""
"创建多个对象（`number > 1`）时，可提供名称列表。若列表长度小于对象数量，则最"
"后一个名称会被重复使用；请确保名称唯一性以避免错误。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:919
msgid ""
"Do not confuse the object-level `name` with the `name` keys inside "
"dictionaries like `shape`, `kinematics`, or `behavior`. The latter specify "
"the type of that component, not the object's identifier."
msgstr ""
"请勿将对象级 `name` 与 `shape`、`kinematics`、`behavior` 等字典内部的 `name` "
"键混淆。后者指定该组件的类型，而非对象的标识符。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:922
msgid "**`role`** (`str`, inferred from top-level key)"
msgstr "**`role`**（`str`，从顶层键推断）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:923
msgid ""
"Defines the object's role in the simulation. In YAML configurations, this is "
"inferred from the section it belongs to and normally does not need to be set "
"manually:"
msgstr ""
"定义对象在仿真中的角色。在 YAML 配置中，该值由对象所属的配置区块推断，通常无"
"需手动设置："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:924
msgid ""
"`'robot'`: An active entity typically controlled by behaviors or input "
"commands."
msgstr "`'robot'`：主动实体，通常由行为或输入命令控制。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:925
msgid ""
"`'obstacle'`: A passive entity that may or may not move but is considered "
"during collision detection."
msgstr "`'obstacle'`：被动实体，可静止也可移动，但参与碰撞检测。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:0
msgid "**object kinematics**"
msgstr "**object 运动学**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:931
msgid "Kinematics Models"
msgstr "运动学模型"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:933
msgid ""
"**`diff`**: Differential drive, controlled by linear speed and angular "
"velocity (`[v, omega]`)"
msgstr "**`diff`** — 差速驱动，由线速度和角速度控制（`[v, omega]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:934
msgid ""
"**`omni`**: Omnidirectional, controlled by body-frame forward and lateral "
"speed (`[forward, lateral]`)"
msgstr ""
"**`omni`** — 全向移动，由机体坐标系下的前进和横向速度控制（`[forward, "
"lateral]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:935
msgid ""
"**`omni_angular`**: Omnidirectional with angular control, controlled by body-"
"frame speeds and yaw rate (`[forward, lateral, yaw_rate]`)"
msgstr ""
"**`omni_angular`** — 带角速度控制的全向移动，由机体坐标系下的速度和偏航角速度"
"控制（`[forward, lateral, yaw_rate]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:936
msgid ""
"**`acker`**: Ackermann steering, controlled by linear speed and steering "
"angle (`[v, phi]`)"
msgstr "**`acker`** — 阿克曼转向，由线速度和转向角控制（`[v, phi]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:940
msgid "**`kinematics`** (`dict`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`kinematics`**（`dict`，默认 `None`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:941
msgid "Sets the kinematic model governing the object's movement."
msgstr "设置控制对象运动的运动学模型。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:944
msgid ""
"`'diff'`: Differential drive robot, suitable for robots that can rotate in "
"place (e.g., two-wheel robots). This type of robot is controlled by linear "
"and angular velocity. Optional parameters:"
msgstr ""
"`'diff'`：差速驱动机器人，适用于原地旋转的机器人（如两轮机器人）。通过线速度"
"和角速度控制。可选参数："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:945
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:954
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:963
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:972
msgid ""
"`noise` (bool): whether to add noise to the velocity commands. Default is "
"`False`."
msgstr "`noise`（bool）：是否给速度命令添加噪声。默认为 `False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:946
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:973
msgid ""
"`alpha` (list): noise parameters for velocity commands. Default is `[0.03, "
"0, 0, 0.03]`."
msgstr "`alpha`（列表）：速度命令的噪声参数。默认值为 `[0.03, 0, 0, 0.03]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:953
msgid ""
"`'omni'`: Omnidirectional movement, allowing movement in any direction "
"without changing orientation. This type of robot is controlled by body-frame "
"velocities `[forward, lateral]`. Orientation (theta) is preserved but not "
"updated. Optional parameters:"
msgstr ""
"`'omni'`：全向运动，允许在任意方向移动而不改变朝向。此类机器人通过机体坐标系"
"速度 `[forward, lateral]` 控制。朝向角（theta）保持不变。可选参数："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:955
msgid ""
"`alpha` (list): noise parameters for velocity commands `[alpha_forward, "
"alpha_lateral]`. Default is `[0.03, 0.03]`."
msgstr ""
"`alpha`（列表）：速度命令的噪声参数 `[alpha_forward, alpha_lateral]`。默认值"
"为 `[0.03, 0.03]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:962
msgid ""
"`'omni_angular'`: Omnidirectional movement with angular velocity control. "
"Extends `omni` by adding a yaw rate channel that integrates orientation "
"(theta). This type of robot is controlled by body-frame velocities "
"`[forward, lateral, yaw_rate]`. Optional parameters:"
msgstr ""
"`'omni_angular'`：带角速度控制的全向运动。在 `omni` 基础上增加偏航角速度通道"
"以积分朝向角（theta）。此类机器人通过机体坐标系速度 `[forward, lateral, "
"yaw_rate]` 控制。可选参数："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:964
msgid ""
"`alpha` (list): noise parameters for velocity commands `[alpha_forward, "
"alpha_lateral, alpha_yaw]`. Default is `[0.03, 0.03, 0.03]`."
msgstr ""
"`alpha`（列表）：速度命令的噪声参数 `[alpha_forward, alpha_lateral, "
"alpha_yaw]`。默认值为 `[0.03, 0.03, 0.03]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:971
msgid ""
"`'acker'`: Ackermann steering, typical for car-like vehicles requiring a "
"turning radius."
msgstr "`'acker'`：阿克曼转向，典型用于类车辆，需要转向半径。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:974
msgid ""
"`mode` (str): steering mode, either `steer` or `angular`. Default is `steer`."
msgstr "`mode`（str）：转向模式，为 `steer` 或 `angular`。默认为 `steer`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:975
msgid "`steer`: the object is controlled by linear and steer angle."
msgstr "`steer`：对象通过线速度和转向角控制。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:976
msgid "`angular`: the object is controlled by linear and angular velocity."
msgstr "`angular`：对象通过线速度和角速度控制。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:984
msgid ""
"**`vel_min`** (`list` of `float`, default: `[-1, -1]`) and **`vel_max`** "
"(`list` of `float`, default: `[1, 1]`)"
msgstr ""
"**`vel_min`**（`float` 列表，默认值：`[-1, -1]`）和 **`vel_max`**（`float` 列"
"表，默认值：`[1, 1]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:985
msgid ""
"Set the minimum and maximum velocity limits for each control dimension "
"(e.g., linear and angular velocities). These constraints ensure the object's "
"motion stays within feasible and safe bounds."
msgstr ""
"设置每个控制维度的最小和最大速度限制（例如线速度和角速度）。这些约束确保对象"
"的运动保持在可行且安全的范围内。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:988
msgid "**`acce`** (`list` of `float`, default: `[inf, inf]`)"
msgstr "**`acce`**（`float` 列表，默认值：`[inf, inf]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:989
msgid ""
"Defines acceleration limits as the maximum change in velocity per time step "
"for each control dimension. This parameter simulates the physical "
"limitations of the object's motion capabilities."
msgstr ""
"定义加速度限制，即每个控制维度在每个时间步内的最大速度变化。此参数模拟对象运"
"动能力的物理限制。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:992
msgid "**`angle_range`** (`list` of `float`, default: `[-pi, pi]`)"
msgstr "**`angle_range`**（`float` 列表，默认：`[-pi, pi]`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:993
msgid ""
"Specifies the allowed range of orientation angles `[min, max]` in radians. "
"The object's orientation angle `theta` is wrapped within this range to "
"maintain consistency."
msgstr ""
"指定允许的朝向角范围 `[min, max]`（弧度）。对象的朝向角 `theta` 会被归整到此"
"范围内以保持一致性。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:996
msgid "**`goal_threshold`** (`float`, default: `0.1`)"
msgstr "**`goal_threshold`**（`float`，默认：`0.1`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:997
msgid ""
"Determines the proximity threshold to the goal at which the object is "
"considered to have arrived. Once within this distance, arrival behaviors or "
"state changes may be triggered."
msgstr ""
"确定对象被认为已到达目标的距离阈值。一旦在此距离范围内，可能会触发到达行为或"
"状态变化。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1009
msgid ""
"When using the `acker` kinematics model, ensure that the `wheelbase` "
"parameter is set in the `shape` configuration."
msgstr ""
"使用 `acker` 运动学模型时，请确保在 `shape` 配置中设置 `wheelbase` 参数。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:0
msgid "**object shape**"
msgstr "**object 形状**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1018
msgid "**`circle`**: Round shape (`radius`, `center`)"
msgstr "**`circle`** — 圆形（`radius`、`center`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1019
msgid "**`rectangle`**: Rectangular shape (`length`, `width`, `wheelbase`)"
msgstr "**`rectangle`** — 矩形（`length`、`width`、`wheelbase`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1020
msgid "**`polygon`**: Custom shape (`vertices`, `is_convex`)"
msgstr "**`polygon`** — 自定义多边形（`vertices`、`is_convex`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1021
msgid "**`linestring`**: Line segments (`vertices`)"
msgstr "**`linestring`** — 线段（`vertices`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1025
msgid "**`shape`** (`dict`, default: `{name: circle}`)"
msgstr "**`shape`**（`dict`，默认 `{name: circle}`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1026
msgid ""
"Determines the geometric shape used for collision detection and "
"visualization in the original state. If `shape` is omitted entirely, the "
"object falls back to a circle of `radius: 1` centered at `[0, 0]`; the "
"`radius: 0.2` below is the default only when a `circle` shape is given "
"without an explicit `radius`."
msgstr ""
"决定初始状态下用于碰撞检测和可视化的几何形状。如果完全省略 `shape`，对象将回"
"退为以 `[0, 0]` 为中心、`radius: 1` 的圆；下面的 `radius: 0.2` 仅在给定 "
"`circle` 形状但未显式指定 `radius` 时作为默认值。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1028
msgid "**Supported Shapes:**"
msgstr "**支持的形状：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1030
msgid "**`'circle'`**: Represents a circular shape."
msgstr "**`'circle'`**：圆形。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1031
msgid "**`radius`** (`float`): Radius of the circle. Default is `0.2`."
msgstr "**`radius`**（`float`）：圆半径，默认 `0.2`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1032
msgid ""
"**`center`** (`list`): Body-frame `[x, y]` offset of the circle center. It "
"rotates with the object's heading. Default is `[0, 0]`. For an Ackermann "
"circle, the effective center is additionally shifted forward by `wheelbase / "
"2`."
msgstr ""
"**`center`**（`list`）：圆心在机体坐标系中的 `[x, y]` 偏移，会随对象朝向旋"
"转。默认值为 `[0, 0]`。对于阿克曼圆形，实际圆心还会向前偏移 `wheelbase / 2`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1033
msgid ""
"**`random_shape`** (`bool`): Whether to generate a random radius. Default is "
"`False`."
msgstr "**`random_shape`**（`bool`）：是否随机半径，默认 `False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1034
msgid ""
"**`radius_range`** (`list`): Range `[min_radius, max_radius]` for random "
"radius generation if `random_shape` is `True`. Default is `[0.1, 1.0]`."
msgstr ""
"**`radius_range`**（`list`）：当 `random_shape` 为 `True` 时用于随机半径生成"
"的范围 `[min_radius, max_radius]`。默认值为 `[0.1, 1.0]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1035
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1045
msgid ""
"**`wheelbase`** (`float`): Wheelbase of the Ackermann steering vehicle. "
"Required when using `'acker'` kinematics. Default is `None`."
msgstr ""
"**`wheelbase`**（`float`）：阿克曼转向车辆的轴距，使用 `'acker'` 时必填，默"
"认 `None`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1042
msgid "**`'rectangle'`**: Represents a rectangular shape."
msgstr "**`'rectangle'`**：矩形。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1043
msgid ""
"**`length`** (`float`): Length of the rectangle along the x-axis. Default is "
"`1.0`."
msgstr "**`length`**（`float`）：x 轴方向长度，默认 `1.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1044
msgid ""
"**`width`** (`float`): Width of the rectangle along the y-axis. Default is "
"`1.0`."
msgstr "**`width`**（`float`）：y 轴方向宽度，默认 `1.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1052
msgid ""
"**`'polygon'`**: Represents a polygonal shape defined by a list of vertices."
msgstr "**`'polygon'`**：由顶点列表定义的多边形。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1053
msgid ""
"**`vertices`** (`list`): List of vertices defining the polygon in the format "
"`[[x1, y1], [x2, y2], ...]`, if not provided, a random polygon will be "
"generated."
msgstr ""
"**`vertices`**（列表）：定义多边形的顶点列表，格式 `[[x1, y1], ...]`。若未提"
"供则生成随机多边形。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1054
msgid ""
"**`random_shape`** (`bool`): Whether to generate a series of random "
"polygons. Default is `False`."
msgstr "**`random_shape`**（`bool`）：是否生成一系列随机多边形，默认 `False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1055
msgid ""
"**`is_convex`** (`bool`): Whether to generate a series of random convex "
"polygons. Default is `False`."
msgstr "**`is_convex`**（`bool`）：是否生成一系列随机凸多边形，默认 `False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1056
msgid ""
"parameters for random polygon generation, see {py:func}"
"`~irsim.lib.algorithm.generation.random_generate_polygon` for more details. "
"Parameters include `number `, `center_range `, `avg_radius_range `, "
"`irregularity_range `, `spikeyness_range `, `num_vertices_range `."
msgstr ""
"随机多边形生成的参数，更多细节参见 {py:func}"
"`~irsim.lib.algorithm.generation.random_generate_polygon`。参数包括 `number "
"`、`center_range `、`avg_radius_range `、`irregularity_range `、"
"`spikeyness_range `、`num_vertices_range `。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1075
msgid ""
"**`'linestring'`**: Represents a line string shape defined by a list of "
"vertices. Similar to a polygon but generates a line string."
msgstr "**`'linestring'`**：由顶点列表定义的折线，类似多边形但生成的是一串线。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1076
msgid ""
"**`vertices`** (`list`): List of vertices defining the line string in the "
"format `[[x1, y1], [x2, y2], ...]`."
msgstr "**`vertices`**（列表）：定义线串的顶点列表，格式 `[[x1, y1], ...]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1077
msgid ""
"**`random_shape`** (`bool`): Whether to generate a series of random line "
"strings (polygon). Default is `False`."
msgstr ""
"**`random_shape`**（`bool`）：是否生成随机线串（多边形），默认 `False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1078
msgid ""
"**`is_convex`** (`bool`): Whether to generate a series of random convex line "
"strings (polygons). Default is `True`."
msgstr "**`is_convex`**（`bool`）：是否生成随机凸线串（多边形），默认 `True`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1079
msgid ""
"parameters for random line string generation (polygon), see {py:func}"
"`~irsim.lib.algorithm.generation.random_generate_polygon` for more details. "
"Parameters include `number `, `center_range `, `avg_radius_range `, "
"`irregularity_range `, `spikeyness_range `, `num_vertices_range `."
msgstr ""
"随机折线（多边形）生成的参数，更多细节参见 {py:func}"
"`~irsim.lib.algorithm.generation.random_generate_polygon`。参数包括 `number "
"`、`center_range `、`avg_radius_range `、`irregularity_range `、"
"`spikeyness_range `、`num_vertices_range `。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:0
msgid "**object behavior**"
msgstr "**object 行为**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1102
msgid "Behavior Systems"
msgstr "行为系统"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1104
msgid ""
"**`behavior`**: `dash` (move toward the goal directly), `rvo` (reciprocal "
"velocity obstacles), `sfm` (social force model)"
msgstr ""
"**`behavior`**：`dash`（直接朝目标移动）、`rvo`（互惠速度障碍）、`sfm`（社会"
"力模型）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1105
msgid "**`group_behavior`**: `orca` (optimal reciprocal collision avoidance)"
msgstr "**`group_behavior`**：`orca`（最优互惠碰撞避免）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1106
msgid "**`static`**: Immobile objects (`True`/`False`)"
msgstr "**`static`** — 静止对象（`True`/`False`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1110
msgid "**`behavior`** (`dict`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`behavior`**（`dict`，默认 `None`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1111
msgid ""
"Configures the movement behavior of the object. Behaviors can be simple or "
"complex and may include additional parameters."
msgstr "配置对象的运动行为，可为简单或复杂策略，并可包含额外参数。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1114
msgid "`'dash'`: Moves directly toward the goal at maximum allowable speed."
msgstr "`'dash'`：以最大允许速度直接朝目标移动。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1115
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1128
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1156
msgid ""
"`wander` (bool/`False`): Whether to add random wandering to the movement. If "
"`True`, the object will have a random goal when reach current goal."
msgstr ""
"`wander`（bool/`False`）：是否加入随机游走。若为 `True`，对象到达当前目标后会"
"随机分配新目标。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1116
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1129
msgid ""
"`loop` (bool/`False`): Whether to loop through waypoints continuously. If "
"`True`, the object will restart from the first waypoint after reaching the "
"last one."
msgstr ""
"`loop`（bool/`False`）：是否循环导航路径点。若为 `True`，对象到达最后一个路径"
"点后会从第一个路径点重新开始。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1117
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1130
msgid ""
"`target_roles` (str/`all`): Only the objects with the target role will be "
"applied to the behavior. Currently, you can set the target role as `robot` "
"or `obstacle`."
msgstr ""
"`target_roles`（str/`all`）：仅对具有目标角色的对象应用该行为。当前可设为 "
"`robot` 或 `obstacle`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1118
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1131
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1157
msgid "`range_low`(list/`[0, 0, -3.14]`): Lower bounds for random wandering."
msgstr "`range_low`（列表）：随机游走下界，默认 `[0, 0, -3.14]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1119
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1132
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1158
msgid "`range_high`(list/`[10, 10, 3.14]`): Upper bounds for random wandering."
msgstr "`range_high`（列表）：随机游走上界，默认 `[10, 10, 3.14]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1120
msgid ""
"`angle_tolerance` (float/`0.1`): Tolerance for orientation alignment with "
"`diff`, `acker`, and `omni_angular` kinematics."
msgstr ""
"`angle_tolerance`（float）：`diff`、`acker`、`omni_angular` 运动学的朝向校准"
"容差，默认 `0.1`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1122
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1143
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1166
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1181
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1217
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1255
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1274
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1298
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1307
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1332
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1348
#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1422
msgid "**Example:**"
msgstr "**示例：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1127
msgid ""
"`'rvo'`: Implements Reciprocal Velocity Obstacles for collision avoidance "
"among multiple moving objects. Support kinematics are `diff` and `omni`."
msgstr "`'rvo'`：实现多动态体避碰的 RVO 算法，支持 `diff` 与 `omni` 运动学。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1133
msgid "`vxmax` (float/`1.5`): Maximum linear velocity in x axis."
msgstr "`vxmax`（float）：x 轴最大线速度，默认 `1.5`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1134
msgid "`vymax` (float/`1.5`): Maximum linear velocity in y axis."
msgstr "`vymax`（float）：y 轴最大线速度，默认 `1.5`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1135
msgid "`acce` (float/`1.0`): Maximum acceleration."
msgstr "`acce`（float）：最大加速度，默认 `1.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1136
msgid "`factor` (float/`1.0`): Factor for the RVO algorithm."
msgstr "`factor`（float）：RVO 算法因子，默认 `1.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1137
msgid ""
"`mode` (str/`rvo`): Mode for RVO algorithm, either `rvo`, `hrvo`, or `vo`."
msgstr "`mode`（str）：RVO 算法模式，可选 `rvo`、`hrvo`、`vo`，默认 `rvo`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1138
msgid ""
"`rvo`: Reciprocal Velocity Obstacles. For multi-agent collision avoidance."
msgstr "`rvo`：互惠速度障碍法，用于多智能体避碰。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1139
msgid ""
"`hrvo`: Hybrid Reciprocal Velocity Obstacles. Combine RVO with VO to avoid "
"deadlocks."
msgstr "`hrvo`：混合 RVO，将 RVO 与 VO 结合以减少死锁。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1140
msgid "`vo`: Velocity Obstacles. For obstacle avoidance."
msgstr "`vo`：速度障碍，用于避障。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1141
msgid ""
"`neighbor_threshold` (float/`3.0`): Distance threshold to filter the "
"neighbors to the self robot."
msgstr "`neighbor_threshold`（float）：筛选邻居的距离阈值，默认 `3.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1148
msgid ""
"`'sfm'`: Implements the Social Force Model for reactive pedestrian-style "
"avoidance. Supported kinematics are `diff` and `omni`."
msgstr ""
"`'sfm'`：实现社会力模型，用于反应式行人风格避障。支持 `diff` 和 `omni` 运动"
"学。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1151
msgid "**`group_behavior`** (`dict`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`group_behavior`**（`dict`，默认 `None`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1152
msgid ""
"Group-level behavior for all objects within the same group. This is more "
"efficient for coordinated behaviors (like swarm or crowd simulation) as it "
"computes actions for all members in a single step. Must include `name` plus "
"behavior-specific parameters."
msgstr ""
"同组内所有对象的群体行为。对于协同行为（如群体或人群仿真）更高效，因为它在单"
"步中为所有成员计算动作。必须包含 `name` 及行为特定参数。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1155
msgid ""
"`'orca'`: Optimal Reciprocal Collision Avoidance (ORCA) for multi-agent "
"navigation. Requires `pyrvo` package (`pip install pyrvo`). The simulation "
"will attempt to import it only when this behavior is used."
msgstr ""
"`'orca'`：用于多智能体导航的最优互惠碰撞避免（ORCA）。需要 `pyrvo` 包（`pip "
"install pyrvo`）。仅在使用该行为时仿真才会尝试导入它。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1159
msgid "`neighborDist` (float/`15.0`): Max distance to search for neighbors."
msgstr "`neighborDist`（float/`15.0`）：搜索邻居的最大距离。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1160
msgid "`maxNeighbors` (int/`10`): Max number of neighbors to consider."
msgstr "`maxNeighbors`（int/`10`）：考虑的邻居数量上限。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1161
msgid ""
"`timeHorizon` (float/`20.0`): Time horizon for computing safe velocities "
"with respect to other agents."
msgstr ""
"`timeHorizon`（float/`20.0`）：相对于其他智能体计算安全速度的时间范围。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1162
msgid ""
"`timeHorizonObst` (float/`10.0`): Time horizon for computing safe velocities "
"with respect to static obstacles."
msgstr ""
"`timeHorizonObst`（float/`10.0`）：相对于静态障碍物计算安全速度的时间范围。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1163
msgid "`safe_radius` (float/`0.1`): Additional safety radius padding."
msgstr "`safe_radius`（float/`0.1`）：额外的安全半径填充。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1164
msgid ""
"`maxSpeed` (float/`None`): Max speed for the agents. If `None`, uses the "
"object's `vel_max`."
msgstr ""
"`maxSpeed`（float/`None`）：智能体最大速度。若为 `None`，使用对象的 "
"`vel_max`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1178
msgid ""
"**`static`**:   A boolean indicating whether the object is static (does not "
"move). Static objects ignore kinematics and behaviors, remaining at their "
"initial state."
msgstr ""
"**`static`**：布尔值，表示对象是否静止。静止对象忽略运动学与行为，保持初始状"
"态。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:0
msgid "**object sensors**"
msgstr "**object 传感器**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1192
msgid ""
"**`lidar2d`**: 2D laser scanner (`range_min/max`, `angle_range`, `noise`)"
msgstr "**`lidar2d`** — 2D 激光雷达（`range_min/max`、`angle_range`、`noise`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1193
msgid ""
"**`fmcw_lidar2d`**: 2D FMCW LiDAR (`range/radial_velocity`, "
"`motion_compensate`, Doppler visualization)"
msgstr ""
"**`fmcw_lidar2d`** —— 2D FMCW 激光雷达（`range/radial_velocity`、"
"`motion_compensate`、多普勒可视化）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1194
msgid "**`fov`**: Field of view angle (radians)"
msgstr "**`fov`** — 视场角（弧度）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1195
msgid "**`fov_radius`**: Maximum detection distance"
msgstr "**`fov_radius`** — 最大探测距离"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1199
msgid ""
"**`sensors`**:   Attaches sensors to the object for environmental "
"perception. Each sensor is defined by a dictionary indicating its type and "
"specific parameters. Currently supported sensor `name` (or `type`) include:"
msgstr ""
"**`sensors`**：为对象挂载传感器以感知环境。每个传感器以字典形式描述其类型与参"
"数，目前支持："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1201
msgid ""
"`lidar2d`: 2D LiDAR sensor for distance measurements. Parameters include:"
msgstr "`lidar2d`：用于距离测量的 2D LiDAR，参数包括："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1202
msgid "`range_min` (float/`0.0`): Minimum detection range."
msgstr "`range_min`（float）：最小探测距离，默认 `0.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1203
msgid "`range_max` (float/`10.0`): Maximum detection range."
msgstr "`range_max`（float）：最大探测距离，默认 `10.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1204
msgid "`angle_range` (float/`pi`): Total angle range of the sensor."
msgstr "`angle_range`（float）：传感器覆盖角度，默认 `pi`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1205
msgid "`number` (int/`100`): Number of laser beams."
msgstr "`number`（int）：激光束数量，默认 `100`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1206
msgid "`scan_time` (float/`0.1`): Time taken for one complete scan."
msgstr "`scan_time`（float）：完成一次扫描的时间，默认 `0.1`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1207
msgid "`noise` (bool/`False`): Whether noise is added to measurements."
msgstr "`noise`（bool）：测量是否加入噪声，默认 `False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1208
msgid ""
"`std` (float/`0.2`): Standard deviation for range noise if `noise` is `True`."
msgstr "`std`（float）：当 `noise=True` 时距离噪声的标准差，默认 `0.2`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1209
msgid ""
"`angle_std` (float/`0.02`): Standard deviation for angle noise if `noise` is "
"`True`."
msgstr "`angle_std`（float）：`noise=True` 时的角度噪声标准差，默认 `0.02`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1210
msgid ""
"`offset` (list/`[0, 0, 0]`): Offset of the sensor from the object's position "
"(x, y, theta)."
msgstr ""
"`offset`（列表）：传感器相对对象位置 (x, y, theta) 的偏移，默认 `[0, 0, 0]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1211
msgid ""
"`has_velocity` (bool/`False`): Whether measures the lidar point velocity."
msgstr "`has_velocity`（bool）：是否测量点速度，默认 `False`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1213
msgid ""
"Visualization options go under the sensor's **`plot:`** sub-dict (flat top-"
"level keys are still accepted for backward compatibility):"
msgstr ""
"可视化选项位于传感器的 **`plot:`** 子字典下（为向后兼容，仍接受扁平的顶层"
"键）："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1214
msgid "`alpha` (float/`0.3`): Transparency for plotting."
msgstr "`alpha`（float）：绘图透明度，默认 `0.3`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1215
msgid "`color` (str/`r`): Color of the sensor."
msgstr "`color`（str）：传感器颜色，默认 `r`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1234
msgid ""
"`fmcw_lidar2d`: Simplified 2D FMCW LiDAR for range and radial Doppler "
"measurements. It reuses the beam geometry of `lidar2d` and adds two "
"functional parameters:"
msgstr ""
"`fmcw_lidar2d`：用于距离和径向多普勒测量的简化 2D FMCW 激光雷达。它复用 "
"`lidar2d` 的波束几何，并新增两个功能参数："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1235
msgid ""
"`motion_compensate` (bool/`False`): Whether to remove ego-motion from the "
"measured radial velocity."
msgstr ""
"`motion_compensate`（bool/`False`）：是否从测得的径向速度中消除自身运动。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1236
msgid ""
"`velocity_noise_std` (float/`0.0`): Standard deviation of Gaussian noise on "
"radial velocity."
msgstr "`velocity_noise_std`（float/`0.0`）：径向速度上高斯噪声的标准差。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1238
msgid ""
"All visualization options go under the sensor's **`plot:`** sub-dict (same "
"convention as `lidar2d` and object `plot:`). Flat top-level keys are still "
"accepted for backward compatibility."
msgstr ""
"所有可视化选项位于传感器的 **`plot:`** 子字典下（与 `lidar2d` 和对象的 "
"`plot:` 约定相同）。为向后兼容，仍接受扁平的顶层键。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1239
msgid ""
"`velocity_color` (bool/`True`): Whether to color valid beams by radial "
"velocity."
msgstr "`velocity_color`（bool/`True`）：是否按径向速度为有效波束着色。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1240
msgid ""
"`velocity_color_max` (float/`2.0`): Velocity magnitude where the plotting "
"color saturates."
msgstr "`velocity_color_max`（float/`2.0`）：绘图颜色饱和时对应的速度大小。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1241
msgid "`velocity_linewidth` (float/`2.5`): Plot line width for valid returns."
msgstr "`velocity_linewidth`（float/`2.5`）：有效回波的绘图线宽。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1242
msgid "`no_hit_linewidth` (float/`0.8`): Plot line width for invalid beams."
msgstr "`no_hit_linewidth`（float/`0.8`）：无效波束的绘图线宽。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1243
msgid "`no_hit_alpha` (float/`0.03`): Plot transparency for invalid beams."
msgstr "`no_hit_alpha`（float/`0.03`）：无效波束的绘图透明度。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1244
msgid ""
"`show_velocity_markers` (bool/`True`): Whether to draw colored hit markers "
"at valid endpoints."
msgstr ""
"`show_velocity_markers`（bool/`True`）：是否在有效端点处绘制彩色命中标记。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1245
msgid ""
"`velocity_marker_size` (float/`36`): Plot marker size for valid endpoints."
msgstr "`velocity_marker_size`（float/`36`）：有效端点的绘图标记大小。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1246
msgid ""
"`velocity_marker_edge_color` (str/`black`): Edge color of the endpoint "
"markers."
msgstr "`velocity_marker_edge_color`（str/`black`）：端点标记的边缘颜色。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1247
msgid ""
"`velocity_marker_edge_width` (float/`0.6`): Edge width of the endpoint "
"markers."
msgstr "`velocity_marker_edge_width`（float/`0.6`）：端点标记的边缘宽度。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1248
msgid ""
"`zero_velocity_color` (str/`cyan`): Plot color used for near-zero radial "
"velocity."
msgstr "`zero_velocity_color`（str/`cyan`）：用于接近零径向速度的绘图颜色。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1249
msgid ""
"`positive_velocity_color` (str/`crimson`): Plot color used for positive "
"radial velocity."
msgstr "`positive_velocity_color`（str/`crimson`）：用于正径向速度的绘图颜色。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1250
msgid ""
"`negative_velocity_color` (str/`royalblue`): Plot color used for negative "
"radial velocity."
msgstr ""
"`negative_velocity_color`（str/`royalblue`）：用于负径向速度的绘图颜色。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1251
msgid "`no_hit_color` (str/`lightgray`): Plot color used for invalid beams."
msgstr "`no_hit_color`（str/`lightgray`）：用于无效波束的绘图颜色。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1253
msgid ""
"The scan output adds `radial_velocity` and `valid` arrays on top of the "
"standard LiDAR angular metadata."
msgstr ""
"扫描输出在标准激光雷达角度元数据的基础上，增加了 `radial_velocity` 和 "
"`valid` 数组。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1271
msgid ""
"**`fov`** and **`fov_radius`**:   Define the field of view (FOV) for the "
"object's sensors. The FOV is the angular range within which the sensor can "
"detect objects. The `fov` parameter specifies the angular range in radians, "
"while `fov_radius` sets the maximum detection distance."
msgstr ""
"**`fov`** 和 **`fov_radius`**：定义对象传感器的视场（FOV）。FOV 是传感器可检"
"测对象的角度范围。`fov` 参数以弧度指定角度范围，`fov_radius` 设置最大检测距"
"离。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:0
msgid "**object mode**"
msgstr "**object 模式**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1286
msgid "**`arrive_mode`**: Goal detection (`position`, `state`)"
msgstr "**`arrive_mode`** — 目标判定方式（`position`、`state`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1287
msgid "**`unobstructed`**: Ignore collisions (`True`/`False`)"
msgstr "**`unobstructed`** — 忽略碰撞（`True`/`False`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1291
msgid "**`arrive_mode`** (`str`, default: `'position'`)"
msgstr "**`arrive_mode`**（`str`，默认 `'position'`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1292
msgid ""
"Chooses the method for determining if the object has arrived at its goal:"
msgstr "选择判定对象是否到达目标的方法："

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1295
msgid ""
"`'position'`: Arrival is based solely on proximity to the goal position "
"(`[x, y]`)."
msgstr "`'position'`：仅根据与目标位置 (`[x, y]`) 的距离判断。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1296
msgid ""
"`'state'`: Considers both position and orientation in the arrival check "
"(`[x, y, theta]`)."
msgstr "`'state'`：同时考虑位置与朝向 (`[x, y, theta]`)。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1304
msgid "**`unobstructed`** (`bool`, default: `False`)"
msgstr "**`unobstructed`**（`bool`，默认 `False`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1305
msgid ""
"When set to `True`, this object is treated as having an unobstructed path, "
"ignoring collisions with other objects and obstacles. This can be useful for "
"testing or for objects that must not be impeded."
msgstr ""
"当设为 `True` 时，该对象被视为无障碍，忽略与其他对象和障碍物的碰撞，适合测试"
"或需要不被阻挡的对象。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:0
msgid "**object visualization**"
msgstr "**object 可视化**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1318
msgid "**`color`**: Object color (`'r'`, `'blue'`, `'k'`)"
msgstr "**`color`** — 对象颜色（`'r'`、`'blue'`、`'k'` 等）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1319
msgid "**`description`**: Image file (`'car_blue.png'`, `'diff_robot0.png'`)"
msgstr ""
"**`description`** — 图像文件（如 `'car_blue.png'`、`'diff_robot0.png'`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1320
msgid "**`plot`**: Advanced display options"
msgstr "**`plot`** — 进阶显示选项"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1321
msgid "**Object**: Appearance (`obj_color`, `obj_alpha`, `obj_linestyle`)"
msgstr "**Object** — 外观（`obj_color`、`obj_alpha`、`obj_linestyle`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1322
msgid "**Goal**: Goal markers (`show_goal`, `goal_color`, `show_goal_text`)"
msgstr "**Goal** — 目标标记（`show_goal`、`goal_color`、`show_goal_text`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1323
msgid "**Trail**: Object trails (`show_trail`, `keep_trail_length`)"
msgstr "**Trail** — 轨迹点（`show_trail`、`keep_trail_length`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1324
msgid "**Trajectory**: Path lines (`show_trajectory`, `keep_traj_length`)"
msgstr "**Trajectory** — 路径线（`show_trajectory`、`keep_traj_length`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1325
msgid "**Sensors**: Sensor display (`show_sensor`, `show_fov`)"
msgstr "**Sensors** — 传感器显示（`show_sensor`、`show_fov`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1329
msgid "**`color`** (`str`, default: inferred from role and kinematics)"
msgstr "**`color`**（`str`，默认从角色和运动学推断）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1330
msgid ""
"Specifies the object's color in visualizations for easy identification. "
"Robots with registered kinematics use the color defined by the kinematics "
"handler; obstacles default to black. Detailed color options can be found in "
"[matplotlib color](https://matplotlib.org/stable/gallery/color/"
"named_colors.html)."
msgstr ""
"指定对象在可视化中的颜色，便于识别。带有已注册运动学的机器人使用运动学处理器"
"定义的颜色；障碍物默认使用黑色。详细颜色选项见 [matplotlib color](https://"
"matplotlib.org/stable/gallery/color/named_colors.html)。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1338
msgid "**`description`** (`str`, default: `None`)"
msgstr "**`description`**（`str`，默认 `None`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1339
msgid ""
"Provides an image for representing the object graphically. Supports image "
"files located in world/description. You can also set the absolute path of "
"the image file by your need."
msgstr ""
"提供用于图形展示的图像，可使用 world/description 下的文件，或自定义绝对路径。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1341
msgid "**Available Images:**"
msgstr "**可用图像：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1342
msgid "`car_green.png`: A default image for the ackermann steering vehicle."
msgstr "`car_green.png`：阿克曼车辆默认图。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1343
msgid "`car_blue.png`"
msgstr "`car_blue.png`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1344
msgid "`car_red.png`"
msgstr "`car_red.png`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1345
msgid "`diff_robot0.png`"
msgstr "`diff_robot0.png`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1346
msgid "`diff_robot1.png`"
msgstr "`diff_robot1.png`"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1354
msgid ""
"**`plot`**:   Contains plotting options controlling the visual "
"representation of the object. All plot elements are initially created at the "
"origin and positioned using transforms and data updates during animation "
"updates."
msgstr ""
"**`plot`**：包含控制对象显示的绘图选项。所有绘图元素初始创建在原点，并在动画"
"更新时通过变换与数据更新定位。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1357
msgid "**Object Visualization Properties:**"
msgstr "**对象可视化属性：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1358
msgid ""
"`obj_linestyle` (str/`'-'`): Line style for object outline (e.g., '-', '--', "
"':', '-.')."
msgstr ""
"`obj_linestyle`（str）：对象轮廓线型（如 '-', '--', ':', '-.'），默认 '-'."

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1359
msgid ""
"`obj_zorder` (int): Z-order (drawing layer) for object elements. Default is "
"3 for robot patches, 1 for obstacle patches, and 2 for description images."
msgstr ""
"`obj_zorder`（int）：对象元素的绘制层级。机器人图形默认 3，障碍物图形默认 1，"
"描述图片默认 2。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1360
msgid ""
"`obj_color` (str): Color of the object. Default is the object's color "
"property."
msgstr "`obj_color`（str）：对象颜色，默认沿用 `color`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1361
msgid "`obj_alpha` (float/`1.0`): Transparency of the object (0.0 to 1.0)."
msgstr "`obj_alpha`（float）：对象透明度（0.0-1.0），默认 1.0。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1362
msgid ""
"`obj_linewidth` (float/`1.0`): Width of the object outline in Matplotlib "
"points."
msgstr "`obj_linewidth`（float/`1.0`）：对象轮廓线宽，单位为 Matplotlib 点。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1364
msgid "**Goal Visualization:**"
msgstr "**目标可视化：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1365
msgid "`show_goal` (bool/`False`): Whether to show the goal position."
msgstr "`show_goal`（bool）：是否显示目标位置，默认 False。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1366
msgid ""
"`goal_color` (str): Color of the goal marker. Default is the object's color."
msgstr "`goal_color`（str）：目标标记颜色，默认与对象一致。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1367
msgid ""
"`goal_alpha` (float/`0.5`): Transparency of the goal marker (0.0 to 1.0)."
msgstr "`goal_alpha`（float）：目标透明度，默认 0.5。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1368
msgid "`goal_zorder` (int/`1`): Z-order of the goal marker."
msgstr "`goal_zorder`（int）：目标层级，默认 1。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1369
msgid "`show_goal_text` (bool/`False`): Whether to show the goal text."
msgstr "`show_goal_text`（bool）：是否显示目标位置的文本，默认 False。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1371
msgid "**Text Label Visualization:**"
msgstr "**文本标签可视化：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1372
msgid ""
"`show_text` (bool/`False`): Whether to show text information. By default, "
"the object's abbreviation (e.g., `r0`, `o1`) is displayed. Custom text can "
"be set at runtime via `object.set_text(\"custom label\")`. Pass `None` to "
"reset to the default abbreviation."
msgstr ""
"`show_text`（bool）：是否显示文本信息，默认 False。默认显示对象缩写（如 "
"`r0`、`o1`）。可在运行时通过 `object.set_text(\"自定义文本\")` 设置自定义文"
"本。传入 `None` 可重置为默认缩写。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1373
msgid "`text_color` (str): Color of the text. Default is 'k' (black)."
msgstr "`text_color`（str）：文本颜色，默认 'k'（黑）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1374
msgid "`text_size` (int/`10`): Font size of the text."
msgstr "`text_size`（int）：字体大小，默认 10。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1375
msgid "`text_alpha` (float/`1.0`): Transparency of the text (0.0 to 1.0)."
msgstr "`text_alpha`（float）：文本透明度，默认 1.0。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1376
msgid "`text_zorder` (int/`2`): Z-order of the text."
msgstr "`text_zorder`（int）：文本层级，默认 2。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1377
msgid ""
"`text_position` (list/`[-radius-0.1, radius+0.1]`): Position offset from "
"object center [dx, dy]."
msgstr ""
"`text_position`（列表）：相对对象中心的偏移 `[dx, dy]`，默认 `[-radius-0.1, "
"radius+0.1]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1379
msgid ""
"Similarly, goal text can be customized via `object.set_goal_text(\"custom "
"goal label\")`."
msgstr ""
"同样，目标文本可通过 `object.set_goal_text(\"自定义目标文本\")` 进行自定义。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1381
msgid "**Velocity Arrow Visualization:**"
msgstr "**速度箭头可视化：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1382
msgid "`show_arrow` (bool/`False`): Whether to show the velocity arrow."
msgstr "`show_arrow`（bool）：是否显示速度箭头，默认 False。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1383
msgid "`arrow_color` (str/`\"gold\"`): Color of the arrow."
msgstr "`arrow_color`（str）：箭头颜色，默认 \"gold\"。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1384
msgid "`arrow_length` (float/`0.4`): Length of the arrow."
msgstr "`arrow_length`（float）：箭头长度，默认 0.4。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1385
msgid "`arrow_width` (float/`0.6`): Width of the arrow."
msgstr "`arrow_width`（float）：箭头宽度，默认 0.6。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1386
msgid "`arrow_alpha` (float/`1.0`): Transparency of the arrow (0.0 to 1.0)."
msgstr "`arrow_alpha`（float）：箭头透明度，默认 1.0。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1387
msgid "`arrow_zorder` (int/`3`): Z-order of the arrow."
msgstr "`arrow_zorder`（int/`3`）：箭头的绘制层级。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1389
msgid "**Trajectory Path Visualization:**"
msgstr "**轨迹线可视化：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1390
msgid "`show_trajectory` (bool/`False`): Whether to show the trajectory line."
msgstr "`show_trajectory`（bool）：是否显示路径线，默认 False。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1391
msgid ""
"`traj_color` (str): Color of the trajectory. Default is the object's color."
msgstr "`traj_color`（str）：路径颜色，默认继承对象颜色。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1392
msgid ""
"`traj_style` (str): Line style of the trajectory (e.g., '-', '--', ':', "
"'-.'). Default is \"-\"."
msgstr "`traj_style`（str）：路径线型（如 '-', '--', ':', '-.'），默认 \"-\"。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1393
msgid ""
"`traj_width` (float/object width): Width of the trajectory line. Default is "
"the object's width."
msgstr "`traj_width`（float/对象宽度）：轨迹线宽，默认为对象宽度。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1394
msgid ""
"`traj_alpha` (float/`0.5`): Transparency of the trajectory (0.0 to 1.0)."
msgstr "`traj_alpha`（float）：路径透明度，默认 0.5。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1395
msgid "`traj_zorder` (int/`0`): Z-order for trajectory elements."
msgstr "`traj_zorder`（int）：路径层级，默认 0。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1396
msgid ""
"`keep_traj_length` (int/`0`): Number of steps to keep from the end of "
"trajectory. Default is 0 (keep all steps)."
msgstr "`keep_traj_length`（int）：保留的尾段步数，默认 0（保留全部）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1398
msgid "**Object Trail Visualization:**"
msgstr "**对象轨迹点可视化：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1399
msgid "`show_trail` (bool/`False`): Whether to show object trails."
msgstr "`show_trail`（bool）：是否显示轨迹点，默认 False。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1400
msgid "`trail_freq` (int/`2`): Frequency of trail display (every N steps)."
msgstr "`trail_freq`（int）：轨迹显示频率（每 N 步），默认 2。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1401
msgid "`trail_type` (str): Type of trail shape. Default is the object's shape."
msgstr "`trail_type`（str）：轨迹形状类型，默认与对象形状相同。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1402
msgid ""
"`trail_edgecolor` (str): Edge color of the trail. Default is the object's "
"color."
msgstr "`trail_edgecolor`（str）：轨迹边缘颜色，默认为对象颜色。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1403
msgid "`trail_linewidth` (float/`0.8`): Width of the trail outline."
msgstr "`trail_linewidth`（float）：轨迹线宽，默认 0.8。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1404
msgid "`trail_alpha` (float/`0.7`): Transparency of the trail (0.0 to 1.0)."
msgstr "`trail_alpha`（float）：轨迹透明度，默认 0.7。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1405
msgid "`trail_fill` (bool/`False`): Whether to fill the trail shape."
msgstr "`trail_fill`（bool）：是否填充轨迹形状，默认 False。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1406
msgid ""
"`trail_color` (str): Fill color of the trail. Default is the object's color."
msgstr "`trail_color`（str）：轨迹填充色，默认为对象颜色。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1407
msgid "`trail_zorder` (int/`0`): Z-order for trail elements."
msgstr "`trail_zorder`（int）：轨迹层级，默认 0。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1408
msgid ""
"`keep_trail_length` (int/`0`): Number of steps to keep from the end of "
"trail. Default is 0 (keep all steps)."
msgstr "`keep_trail_length`（int）：保留的轨迹尾段步数，默认 0（保留全部）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1410
msgid "**Sensor Visualization:**"
msgstr "**传感器可视化：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1411
msgid "`show_sensor` (bool/`True`): Whether to show sensor visualizations."
msgstr "`show_sensor`（bool）：是否显示传感器，默认 True。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1413
msgid "**Field of View Visualization:**"
msgstr "**视场可视化：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1414
msgid "`show_fov` (bool/`False`): Whether to show field of view visualization."
msgstr "`show_fov`（bool）：是否显示视场，默认 False。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1415
msgid "`fov_color` (str/`\"lightblue\"`): Fill color of the field of view."
msgstr "`fov_color`（str）：视场填充色，默认 \"lightblue\"。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1416
msgid "`fov_edge_color` (str/`\"blue\"`): Edge color of the field of view."
msgstr "`fov_edge_color`（str）：视场边缘色，默认 \"blue\"。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1417
msgid ""
"`fov_alpha` (float/`0.5`): Transparency of the field of view (0.0 to 1.0)."
msgstr "`fov_alpha`（float）：视场透明度，默认 0.5。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1418
msgid "`fov_zorder` (int/`1`): Z-order of the field of view."
msgstr "`fov_zorder`（int）：视场层级，默认 1。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1420
msgid ""
"**Note:** All visual elements are created at the origin during "
"initialization and positioned using matplotlib transforms (for patches) and "
"set_data methods (for lines) during animation updates."
