#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:0
msgid "**keyboard properties**"
msgstr "**键盘控制**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1498
msgid ""
"**`keyboard`** (`dict`, default: `{}`) Configure keyboard control. Options "
"are read by `KeyboardControl`. The default backend is `pynput`. If `pynput` "
"is unavailable, IR‑SIM automatically falls back to the Matplotlib backend."
msgstr ""
"**`keyboard`**（`dict`，默认值：`{}`）配置键盘控制。选项由 `KeyboardControl` "
"读取。默认后端为 `pynput`。若 `pynput` 不可用，IR‑SIM 会自动回退到 "
"Matplotlib 后端。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1501
msgid "`backend` (`str`/`\"pynput\"`): Keyboard backend."
msgstr "`backend`（`str`）：键盘后端。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1502
msgid ""
"`\"pynput\"`: Global keyboard hook, but works when the Matplotlib window is "
"focused (requires the `pynput` package)."
msgstr ""
"`\"pynput\"`（默认）：全局键盘hook，但需 Matplotlib 窗口聚焦（依赖 `pynput` "
"包）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1503
msgid ""
"`\"mpl\"`: Matplotlib figure key events works when the figure window is "
"focused. (no extra dependency, but may be delayed when there are lots of "
"objects)."
msgstr ""
"`\"mpl\"`：Matplotlib 图窗按键事件，仅在窗口聚焦时生效；无额外依赖，但对象数"
"量多时可能有延迟。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1504
msgid ""
"`global_hook` (`bool`/`False`): With `backend: 'pynput'`, capture keys even "
"if the Matplotlib window is not focused. (only active when the window is "
"focused)."
msgstr ""
"`global_hook`（`bool`/`False`）：当 `backend: 'pynput'` 时，即使 Matplotlib "
"窗口未获得焦点也捕获按键。（仅在窗口获得焦点时生效）。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1505
msgid "`key_lv_max` (`float`/`3.0`): Maximum linear velocity."
msgstr "`key_lv_max`（`float`）：最大线速度，默认 3.0。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1506
msgid "`key_ang_max` (`float`/`1.0`): Maximum angular velocity."
msgstr "`key_ang_max`（`float`）：最大角速度，默认 1.0。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1507
msgid "`key_lv` (`float`/`0.0`): Initial linear velocity."
msgstr "`key_lv`（`float`）：初始线速度，默认 `0.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1508
msgid "`key_ang` (`float`/`0.0`): Initial angular velocity."
msgstr "`key_ang`（`float`）：初始角速度，默认 `0.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1509
msgid ""
"`key_rot` (`float`/`0.0`): Initial rotational velocity (yaw rate for "
"`omni_angular` kinematics)."
msgstr ""
"`key_rot`（`float`）：初始旋转速度（`omni_angular` 运动学下的偏航角速度），默"
"认 `0.0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1510
msgid "`key_id` (`int`/`0`): Initial robot control id."
msgstr "`key_id`（`int`）：初始机器人控制 ID，默认 `0`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1526
msgid "**Keyboard Control Keys:**"
msgstr "**键盘控制按键：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1528
msgid "`w`: Forward"
msgstr "`w` — 前进"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1529
msgid "`s`: Backward"
msgstr "`s` — 后退"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1530
msgid "`a`: Turn left (`diff`/`acker`) or strafe left (`omni`/`omni_angular`)"
msgstr "`a` — 左转（`diff`/`acker`）或左侧平移（`omni`/`omni_angular`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1531
msgid ""
"`d`: Turn right (`diff`/`acker`) or strafe right (`omni`/`omni_angular`)"
msgstr "`d` — 右转（`diff`/`acker`）或右侧平移（`omni`/`omni_angular`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1532
msgid "`q`: Rotate left (yaw rate for `omni_angular`)"
msgstr "`q` — 左旋转（`omni_angular` 的偏航角速度）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1533
msgid "`e`: Rotate right (yaw rate for `omni_angular`)"
msgstr "`e` — 右旋转（`omni_angular` 的偏航角速度）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1534
msgid "`z` / `c`: Decrease / increase maximum angular velocity (`key_ang_max`)"
msgstr "`z` / `c` — 降低 / 提高最大角速度（`key_ang_max`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1535
msgid ""
"`shift+z` / `shift+c`: Decrease / increase maximum linear velocity "
"(`key_lv_max`)"
msgstr "`shift+z` / `shift+c` — 降低 / 提高最大线速度（`key_lv_max`）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1536
msgid "`alt+num`: Change Current Control Robot ID"
msgstr "`alt+num` — 更改当前控制的机器人ID"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1537
msgid "`r`: Reset the Environment"
msgstr "`r` — 重置环境"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1538
msgid "`space`: Toggle Pause/Resume Environment"
msgstr "`space` — 切换暂停/恢复环境"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1539
msgid "`esc`: Quit the Environment (sets quit flag)"
msgstr "`esc` — 退出环境（设置退出标志）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1540
msgid "`x`: Switch Keyboard/Auto Control"
msgstr "`x` — 切换键盘/自动控制"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1541
msgid "`l`: Reload the Environment"
msgstr "`l` — 重新加载环境"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1542
msgid "`F5`: Debug the Environment (fn+f5 for mac)"
msgstr "`F5` — 调试环境（Mac上使用fn+f5）"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1543
msgid "`v`: Save the current figure"
msgstr "`v` — 保存当前图像"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1544
msgid "`y`: Toggle display render window"
