#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1723
msgid "**Configuration Best Practices:**"
msgstr "**配置最佳实践：**"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1725
msgid ""
"**Multiple Objects**: When configuring multiple objects, use the `number` "
"and `distribution` parameters to efficiently generate them. For instance, "
"setting `number: 10` with a `distribution` of `'random'` can quickly "
"populate the simulation with randomly placed objects."
msgstr ""
"**多个对象**：配置多个对象时，使用 `number` 和 `distribution` 参数可高效地生"
"成它们。例如，设置 `number: 10` 并使用 `'random'` 的 `distribution`，可快速在"
"仿真中随机放置大量对象。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1726
msgid ""
"**Dictionary Parameters**: All dictionary-type parameters (e.g., "
"`distribution`, `shape`, `kinematics`, `behavior`) must include a `'name'` "
"key to specify their type. Omitting the `'name'` key will result in default "
"values or errors."
msgstr ""
"**字典参数**：所有字典类型的参数（如 `distribution`、`shape`、`kinematics`、"
"`behavior`）都必须包含 `'name'` 键以指定其类型。省略 `'name'` 键会导致使用默"
"认值或报错。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1727
msgid ""
"**Group Configurations**: By default, objects within the same group share "
"configurations. To customize individual objects within a group, add sub-"
"parameters using `-`. Unspecified objects will inherit the last defined "
"configuration within the group."
msgstr ""
"**分组配置**：同组对象默认共享配置。若需定制，请使用 `-` 添加子参数；未显式配"
"置的对象会继承组内最后一个配置。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1728
msgid ""
"**Kinematics and Velocities**: Ensure that the `velocity` and `vel_max` "
"parameters match the kinematics model. For example, a differential drive "
"robot (`'diff'`) uses `[v, omega]`, an omnidirectional robot (`'omni'`) uses "
"body-frame `[forward, lateral]`, and `'omni_angular'` uses `[forward, "
"lateral, yaw_rate]`."
msgstr ""
"**运动学与速度**：确保 `velocity` 与 `vel_max` 的格式与运动学模型匹配，例如差"
"速 (`'diff'`) 使用 `[v, omega]`，全向 (`'omni'`) 使用机体坐标系 `[forward, "
"lateral]`，`'omni_angular'` 使用 `[forward, lateral, yaw_rate]`。"

#: ../../source/yaml_config/configuration.md:1729
msgid ""
"**Plotting Options**: Customize the visualization of your simulation through "
"the `plot` parameter for each object if the `plot` section is located in the "
"object configuration. If it is located in the root of the object "
"configuration, it will be applied to all objects."
msgstr ""
"**绘图选项**：若 `plot` 位于对象配置内部，可为单个对象定制可视化；若位于对象"
"配置的根级，则应用于所有对象。"
